data.description: Assumable VA Mortgage 2.375% APR -Introducing a spectacular opportunity to own a stunning ground floor condominium in the picturesque Panama City Beach area. Boasting four bedrooms and three bathrooms, this property provides ample space and comfort for all your accommodation needs. With its convenient location just half a mile away from the mesmerizing sandy white beach, you'll have easy access to the coastline's beauty and tranquility.Imagine stepping out of your door and immersing yourself in the scenic bike paths that wind through the vibrant surroundings. This coveted amenity offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities and exploration.Welcome to Nautilus Cove, a gated condominium community that ensures both privacy and security. As you step through the threshold of this ground floor unit, you'll be greeted by newly installed wood look LVP floors that seamlessly enhance the overall aesthetics of the space. The addition of a new water heater adds to the list of recent upgrades, ensuring a hassle-free living experience for the lucky new owner.Convenience is at its finest with this property. Just 1.6 miles from Pier Park, you'll have quick access to a hub of entertainment, dining, and shopping options. Additionally, the proximity to ECP airport, a mere 14 miles away, ensures hassle-free travel experiences for you and your guests.Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity - Act now and make this sought-after property your own, indulging in the unparalleled lifestyle that Panama City Beach has to offer. HOA fees include water and sewer, so no water bill!
